sentences: Michael Rudy Nikkerud (born, 13 March 1986), known professionally as Rudy Nikkerud, is an Australian Pentecostal worship leader and singer in the Planetshakers band.
Rudy currently serves as a pastor in the Planetshakers Church and is also a worship leader of the Planetshakers band.
